summary: VEHICLE WAS IN A MINOR COLLISION.  HIT ANOTHER CAR IN REAR AT LESS THAN 15MPH.  AIR BAGS DEPLOYED HITTING DRIVER.  VERY LITTLE FRONT END DAMAGE.  I DO NOT BELIEVE THAT THE AIR BAGS SHOULD HAVE DEPLOYED, AND I AM CONCERNED FOR OUR EMPLOYEES SAFETY.  THIS IS THE SECOND TIME WE HAVE HAD AN INTREPID DEPLOY AIR BAGS AT UNDER 15MPH.
